    <h2 id="api-reference">CSS Properties</h2>
    <div class="api-reference">
        <h4 id="valid-css-properties-for-custom-animations">Valid CSS Properties for Custom Animations</h4>
        <p>The <code>properties</code> hash accepts the following CSS properties:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Transform Properties:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li><code>transform</code> - Accepts combinations of:
                        <ul>
                            <li><code>translateX(), translateY(), translateZ()</code> - Move in X, Y, or Z axis</li>
                            <li><code>scale(), scaleX(), scaleY()</code> - Scale size</li>
                            <li><code>rotate(), rotateX(), rotateY(), rotateZ()</code> - Rotation</li>
                            <li><code>skew(), skewX(), skewY()</code> - Skew/tilt</li>
                            <li><code>perspective()</code> - 3D depth perspective</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li><strong>Color & Background:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li><code>color</code> - Text color</li>
                    <li><code>background</code> - Background color or gradient</li>
                    <li><code>background_color</code> - Just the background color</li>
                    <li><code>border_color</code> - Border color</li>
                    <li><code>opacity</code> - Transparency (0 to 1)</li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li><strong>Size & Position:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li><code>width</code> - Element width</li>
                    <li><code>height</code> - Element height</li>
                    <li><code>margin</code> - Outer spacing</li>
                    <li><code>padding</code> - Inner spacing</li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li><strong>Visual Effects:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li><code>box_shadow</code> - Shadow effects</li>
                    <li><code>filter</code> - Visual filters like blur, brightness</li>
                    <li><code>backdrop_filter</code> - Background blur effects</li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li><strong>Animation Control:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li><code>duration</code> - Animation length (e.g., "0.3s", "1s")</li>
                    <li><code>timing</code> - Timing function (e.g., "ease", "linear")</li>
                    <li><code>delay</code> - Start delay (e.g., "0.1s")</li>
                    <li><code>iteration</code> - Number of repeats or "infinite"</li>
                    <li><code>direction</code> - Animation direction</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>